{"tid":1546331,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟放低你對光復香港時代革命嘅定義","createTime":"2019-09-06T08:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T08:12:19.000Z","uid":280302,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e1ba82c34ec03fbb5b6556fc8827794fa3a13fc8","tid":1546331,"uid":280302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我先<br />\n光復香港: 係因為香港嘅制度同埋整個政治嘅體制 已經腐壞得好緊要 ，所以我哋要去重新靠自己攞返香港以前嘅光輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n時代革命: 喺回歸中國之後嘅廿幾年， 所有香港人都抱住一啲冇所謂啦嘅心態， 但係開始越嚟越多香港人覺醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />知道自己嘅權利要靠自己去爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢班覺醒咗嘅人無分年齡， 唔單止係屬於一個年齡層嘅人， 所以係整個時代。而且大家都立定決心一定要從最根本去重新改革<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 希望老人家可以生活得開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生活得舒服啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中年人唔需要再面對太大嘅壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有足夠嘅時間去照顧自己嘅身體同埋享受生活， 同埋有一個歡樂嘅家庭時光<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以過一個更加開心難忘嘅學生時光， 少啲讀書壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多啲時間可以去拍下拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然我係A09<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 畢咗業嘅可以有一個更好嘅機遇, 唔再畀老細壓迫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同事可以更加開心地相處, 唔使再有啲辦公室政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未出過社會生存, 寫嘅字都幼稚啲， 我都想睇下大家嘅定義<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sorry for 1999    希望有人會應我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71050005406c23ec2e96392c776320a546fd43dc","tid":1546331,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:49:55.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fg5HKFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFg5HKFh.jpg&h=b79850f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=4ca4d5a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"eb14c06848e1de3dd9181b54d96d0e97d1d595ff","tid":1546331,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:50:34.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1277f84448ed113a14b93515238a2bc35206faab","tid":1546331,"uid":280302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71050005406c23ec2e96392c776320a546fd43dc","tid":1546331,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,